name: Sienar Fleet Systems
Lore: 'Industry leader in fighter production, but produces several other products. Constantly working on advancements o the baseline TIE design.',
Text: 'Deploy on Wakeelmui system. Retrieve 1 Force each time you deploy a TIE. Also, once per turn you may relocate a TIE just lost from table to Used Pile. (Immune to Alter while you occupy Wakeelmui.)',
